{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u904a\u6232\u4e2d\u73a9\u5bb6\u626e\u6f14\u4ea1\u547d\u7d05\u8272\u5c0f\u5df4 \uff08\u5f8c\u7a31\u7d05Van\uff09\u53f8\u6a5f\uff0c\u70ba\u8cfa\u9322\u990a\u5bb6\uff0c\u4e0d\u60dc\u8d85\u901f\u99d5\u99db\u3002\u73a9\u5bb6\u9700\u8981\u4e0a\u4e0b\u79fb\u52d5\uff0c\u907f\u958b\u969c\u7919\u7269\uff0c\u4ee5\u6700\u5feb\u901f\u5ea6\u5230\u9054\u7d42\u9ede\uff01</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In the game, players take on the role of a reckless red minibus (hereafter referred to as &quot;Red Van&quot;) driver , who drives at high speeds to earn money to support their family.\u00a0Players need to move up and down to avoid obstacles and reach the finish line as quickly as possible!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3502610/extras/ezgif-3739546926a01.gif?t=1739275794\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u904a\u6232\u9748\u611f\u4f86\u81ea\u7db2\u4e0a\u591a\u5f35\u8d85\u901f\u7167\u7247\uff0c\u52a0\u4e0a\u88fd\u4f5c\u8005\u4ee5\u5f80\u7684\u7d93\u6b77\uff0c\u7d05Van\u53f8\u6a5f\u6c38\u4e0d\u6e1b\u901f\u8f49\u5f4e\u3002\u7db2\u4e0a\u66f4\u6709\u6539\u5716\u7b11\u7a31\u7d05Van\u53f8\u6a5f\u6bd4\u8d77\u6f2b\u756b\u982d\u6587\u5b57D\u7684\u8cfd\u8eca\u624b\u66f4\u70ba\u53b2\u5bb3\u3002</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The game is inspired by numerous online photos of speeding violations, combined with the creator's past experiences. The Red Van driver never brakes while turning. There are even online memes joking that Red Van drivers are more skilled than the racers in the comic &quot;Initial D.&quot;</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u4e0d\u904e\uff0c\u96a8\u8457\u9999\u6e2f\u7684\u591c\u751f\u6d3b\u6e1b\u5c11\uff0c\u52a0\u4e0a\u9435\u8def\u6108\u8d77\u6108\u591a\uff0c\u7d05Van\u5df2\u6f38\u8da8\u5f0f\u5fae\uff0c\u73a9\u5bb6\u5c31\u53ef\u80fd\u662f\u6700\u5f8c\u4e00\u4ee3\u4ea1\u547d\u7d05Van\u50b3\u5947\u3002</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">However, with the decline of nightlife in Hong Kong and the increasing number of railways, the Red Van has gradually faded away. Players may be the last generation of legendary reckless Red Van drivers.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3502610/extras/asd.png?t=1739275794\" /></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3502610/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1739275794","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3502610/page.bg.jpg?t=1739275794","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3502610/c09a92e99505fa1243a5edb1033bc49b2de2fa92/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1739275794","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3502610/c09a92e99505fa1243a5edb1033bc49b2de2fa92/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1739275794","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u904a\u6232\u4e2d\u73a9\u5bb6\u626e\u6f14\u4ea1\u547d\u7d05\u8272\u5c0f\u5df4 \uff08\u5f8c\u7a31\u7d05Van\uff09\u53f8\u6a5f\uff0c\u70ba\u8cfa\u9322\u990a\u5bb6\uff0c\u4e0d\u60dc\u8d85\u901f\u99d5\u99db\u3002\u73a9\u5bb6\u9700\u8981\u4e0a\u4e0b\u79fb\u52d5\uff0c\u907f\u958b\u969c\u7919\u7269\uff0c\u4ee5\u6700\u5feb\u901f\u5ea6\u5230\u9054\u7d42\u9ede\uff01</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In the game, players take on the role of a reckless red minibus (hereafter referred to as &quot;Red Van&quot;) driver , who drives at high speeds to earn money to support their family.\u00a0Players need to move up and down to avoid obstacles and reach the finish line as quickly as possible!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3502610/extras/ezgif-3739546926a01.gif?t=1739275794